### Get the user playlists
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}
GET {{host}}/playlists
Authorization:  Bearer {{token}}

### Get a single playlist
GET {{host}}/playlists/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Add a new playlist
POST {{host}}/playlists
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

